WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.149
Hey, good morning family!

00:00:01.149 --> 00:00:03.144
I'm excited to be with y'all again today.

00:00:03.144 --> 00:00:09.423
I'm going to do another 'pray with me' video to motivate yourself to pray.

00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:24.120
I started doing these videos because one of the main missions of why God put me on YouTube and what He told me to do was come on here and pray about the end times, Israel, and where we are in the end times.

00:00:27.300 --> 00:00:30.644
We can pray together in the spirit.

00:00:31.138 --> 00:00:39.080
I do it alongside another audience because it doesn't make it so awkward for me, just praying by myself on a camera like this.

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:47.827
This is with sister Billie Brim and with Lynne Hammond, and there are a lot of great prayer warriors that we're going to pray with today.

00:00:49.053 --> 00:01:07.720
It's just been on my heart; I told you all almost a year ago about one of the visions that the Lord showed me about Putin and the escalation of the war, and that this would not just stop with Ukraine.

00:01:08.599 --> 00:01:21.415
The Lord warned me that there would be a strike against Poland and that this would be one of the main things that escalate into World War III through Europe.

00:01:28.103 --> 00:01:31.240
Russia would use a weapon that's never been used before on Poland.

00:01:31.240 --> 00:01:56.560
I asked the Lord because I thought it was nuclear, and the Lord told me, 'This is not a nuclear weapon; this is a weapon that's never been used before.

00:01:56.560 --> 00:02:05.820
' It was massive, and it hit near Warsaw.

00:02:18.782 --> 00:02:25.884
It was a big city with a 'W' I saw in the spirit, but I have an urgency in my spirit that is trying to speed up.

00:02:28.471 --> 00:02:34.400
I believe we're going to see wars and rumors of wars.

00:02:36.338 --> 00:02:49.994
A lot of people wanted to know more about what I saw regarding DNA codes and the virus.

00:02:49.994 --> 00:02:53.805
They're asking if the medicine is bad.

00:02:53.805 --> 00:03:03.330
No, I want everybody to understand what I'm trying to say here.

00:03:03.330 --> 00:03:18.610
Like I said, I'm not coming on here to preach fear; I'm telling you what I see when I pray.

00:03:21.178 --> 00:03:48.924
The Lord gives me these things so we can either delay them, stop them altogether, or they're going to happen regardless, but He's warning me about things that are about to manifest.

00:03:49.753 --> 00:03:58.780
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I'm mandating you to get the weight off.

00:03:58.780 --> 00:04:12.640
' That was a year ago, and He speaks to me way in advance of what He believes is coming.

00:04:13.730 --> 00:04:22.267
He talks to me about the oil, crypto, and many other things, sometimes years in advance.

00:04:22.267 --> 00:04:40.355
This is another thing I really believe we're about to see regarding taking DNA with AI and creating a virus, a superbug, to eliminate obese people.

00:04:52.785 --> 00:04:53.080
It was created because the obesity rates were so astronomical.

00:04:53.080 --> 00:05:08.759
There are things I see that are very dark, and the Lord warns me about what the enemy is planning.

00:05:10.840 --> 00:05:20.929
I don't get in fear over it; I know that Jesus said no weapon formed against me would prosper.

00:05:20.929 --> 00:05:36.460
He wants us to listen to Him and be quick to obey in these last days.

00:05:36.460 --> 00:05:53.168
He may say, 'Don't go to this place,' and if you go, it could cost you your life.

00:05:53.168 --> 00:05:59.985
We need to be quick to pray and obey.

00:06:00.855 --> 00:06:20.880
I told you all I let food dominate me, and I didn't listen last year, but now the Lord is warning me to get the weight off, so I'm working on that.

00:06:20.880 --> 00:06:26.820
He will show you things to come.

00:06:26.820 --> 00:06:51.383
In that last video, I tried to comfort you all to listen to what the Spirit of the Lord is saying about the enemy's plans regarding DNA code.

00:06:59.458 --> 00:07:08.280
I saw the high blood pressure medicine and diabetic medicine, and they were using AI to make a super virus.

00:07:08.280 --> 00:07:11.919
We have authority in this earth.

00:07:11.919 --> 00:07:21.525
Revelation talks about how half of the population of the world will perish.

00:07:21.525 --> 00:07:32.759
A lot of these things are coming for the Tribulation, for Jacob's Trouble, for the seven years.

00:07:47.662 --> 00:07:48.034
I don't believe the church is going to go through that.

00:07:48.034 --> 00:08:07.000
God's not a wife-beater, and I believe we're going to be raptured out of here before all this starts.

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:18.599
People want to know if the financial crisis is going to happen.

00:08:18.599 --> 00:08:33.625
The Lord showed me that a lot of these things will manifest after the Rapture of the church.

00:08:38.927 --> 00:08:56.714
The financial sector and all the major economic struggle will happen after millions of us are raptured out of here, which will cause a great economic crash.

00:08:56.714 --> 00:09:12.136
They will bring in that Beast system, but it didn't happen instantaneously when the Rapture took place.

00:09:25.580 --> 00:09:31.711
The chip and all those things took time to get around and get people ready for it.

00:09:31.711 --> 00:09:51.191
Last night, I was praying and the Lord told me to go on Pastor Paul Begley's channel and watch his video.

00:09:57.347 --> 00:10:09.491
I listened to Mike from Around the World and Pastor Paul Begley talking about the end times, where we are with the red heifer.

00:10:09.491 --> 00:10:39.824
It stood out to me because the prophetic word the Lord gave me was that when Passover comes, there's going to be an acceleration of things beyond what He told me about Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

00:10:59.200 --> 00:10:59.880
This is going to be another time of great acceleration with the economy, the war, and signs in the heavens.

00:10:59.880 --> 00:11:12.090
It sounded to me like they're wanting to sacrifice that pure red heifer on Passover.

00:11:12.090 --> 00:11:33.725
Here we are, according to what I heard Pastor Paul Begley talking about, seeing an acceleration take place at Passover.

00:11:33.725 --> 00:11:41.303
There's fruit of it; they're talking about sacrificing this red heifer now.

00:11:47.657 --> 00:11:47.886
It sounds like a big end-times event.

00:11:47.886 --> 00:11:56.220
Then we have the big American eclipse taking place on the 8th of April.

00:11:56.220 --> 00:12:05.888
It's like a snowball going down a hill, getting bigger and bigger.

00:12:05.888 --> 00:12:08.476
Jesus is coming quickly.

00:12:08.476 --> 00:13:17.910
He said, 'My Son's return for the bride is imminent.

00:13:17.920 --> 00:16:36.030
' It's time for us to get serious.

00:16:36.040 --> 00:20:25.646
I believe we're about to see Gog and Magog, the war with Russia and the hook in the mouth pulling Russia down.

00:20:25.646 --> 00:20:55.669
I'm going to play this prayer video.

00:20:55.679 --> 00:22:09.170
Let's just pray.

00:23:29.806 --> 00:24:57.926
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, we're about to see one of the greatest manifestations of the glory of God that this world has ever seen.

00:24:57.926 --> 00:25:53.883
' Supernatural healings and manifestations of the glory of God are coming before the catching away.

00:25:53.883 --> 00:27:16.210
I believe we're going to see financial breakthroughs for people.

00:27:16.220 --> 00:28:09.816
Bitcoin is already going back up to record highs.

00:28:09.816 --> 00:28:20.039
So, let's get started and pray with Sister Billie here.

00:28:20.039 --> 00:28:29.695
Father, I thank You, Lord.

00:28:29.695 --> 00:28:54.640
We take up Israel now.

00:28:54.640 --> 00:29:01.600
We pray for the military and the Mossad.

00:29:01.600 --> 00:29:32.837
