00:29:32.837 --> 00:31:26.149
Lord, we praise You for Your angelic operation for the nations of the earth.

00:31:26.159 --> 00:32:47.889
America, you shall be saved!

00:32:47.889 --> 00:36:20.430
Spirit of darkness, loose your grip on this nation in Jesus' name.

00:40:10.839 --> 00:40:11.207
We command an outpouring of God across this land, with angelic assistance.

00:40:11.943 --> 00:40:20.931
