00:52:29.635 --> 00:52:30.020
There is help.

00:52:30.020 --> 00:52:36.422
We're making power available through prayers lifted up.

00:52:42.310 --> 00:52:42.620
We pray for healings right now.

00:52:42.620 --> 00:52:48.560
