00:55:59.226 --> 00:58:23.710
I'm convinced the wave that's coming will be twice as high as what we've seen in the past.

00:58:50.920 --> 00:58:52.300
Glory to God!

00:58:52.300 --> 00:59:10.573
We walk in boldness in these end times, with waves of the glory of God delivering people from satanic bondage.

00:59:15.150 --> 00:59:23.343
