00:59:39.500 --> 01:00:08.245
There is a move of God the world has never seen before about to happen—a major outpouring of the Spirit right before the catching away of the church.

01:00:13.067 --> 01:00:34.719
I want you to agree with me right now that there is a major move of God happening in your house, your finances, your marriage, and your life.

01:00:34.719 --> 01:00:46.300
The 'suddenlies' are going to start to happen like popcorn in your life.

01:00:52.079 --> 01:00:52.559
